Two proposed additions to this old-ish thread; I know I could just go ahead and edit the wiki, but since there seem to be disagreement on who is “enough active” to make it to [the list](http://web.archive.org/web/20120129114804/http:/typophile.com/node/19891) I though to post here:

- [Juan Pablo de Gregorio](http://web.archive.org/web/20120129114804/http:/typophile.com/user/619), whose [Los Niches](http://web.archive.org/web/20120129114804/http:/www.veer.com/products/typedetail.aspx?image=UMT0000269) recently went up for sale on Veer;
- [Claudio Piccinini](http://web.archive.org/web/20120129114804/http:/typophile.com/user/1316), who’s got typefaces out for Emigre and Thirstype (and Village, of course);

Cheers.
